{"by":"danish00111","id":47757893,"kids":[47759125],"parent":47739305,"text":"The problem with most &quot;AI study modes&quot; is that they optimize for knowledge transfer. The harder problem is knowledge use, being able to actually apply something under pressure. Reading about how to handle a difficult conversation is not the same as practicing it. Knowing the BATNA framework or some other thing you learn from chatgpt doesn&#x27;t mean you can use it when someone lowballs you and you have 10 seconds to respond.","time":1776114841,"type":"comment"}